transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thanks for calling Viagra. This is Jimmy. How can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Hi, Jimmy. I'm just calling because I wanted to request a refund.

Speaker 1: Okay. Let me see how I can help you with that. Give me one second.

Speaker 2: Am I speaking to Mark?

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: Okay, Mark, I do have your account up.

Speaker 1: It looks like that you got the Viagra 50 milligram.

Speaker 2: It looks like that you got 10 of them.

Speaker 1: Can I ask why do you want a refund if you don't mind?

Speaker 2: It's just not working like how I expected it to work.

Speaker 1: You know what, Mark, I'm looking at what you ordered.

Speaker 2: It looks like you got the Viagra 50 milligrams, but did you order online, Mark?

Speaker 1: I'm just curious.

Speaker 2: Yes, I did.

Speaker 1: Okay, because it looks like that you got the regular generic Viagra.

Speaker 2: Were you trying to get the new and improved AGB when you did your order?

Speaker 1: Yeah, that's what I chose, and it says it on here, too.

Speaker 2: No, you didn't get it.

Speaker 1: I looked at your prescription.

Speaker 2: Do you have the pills in front of you?

Speaker 1: I don't, but it says original new Viagra AGB 50 milligrams.

Speaker 2: No, I'm looking at it.

Speaker 1: You didn't get the AGB.

Speaker 2: I can tell you right now you got the regular generic Viagra.

Speaker 1: So, you know what, let me do this for you.

Speaker 2: I'm going to send you out 10 of the AGB for free and give you an opportunity to try those.

Speaker 1: Okay, because you didn't get that.

Speaker 2: Let me tell you the difference of the ones I'm going to send you compared to the ones you got.

Speaker 1: They're going to be the same white-shaped diamond pills,

Speaker 2: but they're going to have the number 5-0 on the back if you want the 50 milligrams.

Speaker 1: What I can recommend for you, and I can do this for you, too, if you like, Mark,

Speaker 2: I'm going to send you the 100 milligrams.

Speaker 1: And what people do all the time, they'll take the 100 and see how good it works,

Speaker 2: and if they work that good, they'll just break it in half,

Speaker 1: and that will be like a double bang for your buck, too, as well.

Speaker 2: So instead of the 10, you actually have 20 pills because of the 100 milligrams if you break them in half.

Speaker 1: So I'm going to do that for you, okay?

Speaker 2: I'm going to send you out 10 of the 100 milligrams of the AGB,

Speaker 1: and the AGB in this case is going to have the number 1-0-0 on the back

Speaker 2: because you didn't get the AGB or the 50 milligrams,

Speaker 1: but I'm going to give you out 10 of the 100 with no charge.

Speaker 2: And I'm going to give you a few months to try those and make sure you like them, okay?

Speaker 1: Okay, that sounds good.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: So I'll take care of you, Mark.

Speaker 2: No problem.

Speaker 1: So those should be coming to you in the next, I would say, about 7 to 10 days.

Speaker 2: Look for those.

Speaker 1: It's going to be the same label on your bottle, but notice it's going to say 100 on the back of the pill.

Speaker 2: Notice the back of the pill is going to have the number 1-0-0, same white-shaped diamond pill,

Speaker 1: and you're going to see a drastic effect compared to the other ones that you had.

Speaker 2: All right?

Speaker 1: Sounds good.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: Not a problem.

Speaker 1: I'll take care of you.

Speaker 2: My name is Jimmy.

Speaker 1: Unfortunately, sometimes when you do it on the computer, it kind of throws things off.

Speaker 2: So just call us like you did today, and we'll make sure you get the right things going forward.

Speaker 1: And I'm going to update your prescription, but when you do order, you'll get what I'm sending you out now.

Speaker 2: All right?

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Thanks, Jimmy.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: Not a problem.

Speaker 1: Take care.

Speaker 2: You too.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.

Speaker 2: Bye-bye.
